{"tid":1844180,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"賣假口罩嘅藥房要有報應!!","createTime":"2020-01-26T13:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T02:42:20.000Z","uid":339062,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"848a97a4ad1003f2151b0fafe416e66823410386","tid":1844180,"uid":339062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"其實最仆街唔係啲炒價藥房<br />\n而係賣啲冇防疫功能口罩嘅藥房<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老母年廿九買咗幾盒<br />\n年三十我想攞返去鬧爆間藥房點知佢收咗爐<br />\n<br />\n少啲常識好易比你害死！<br />\n最容易受感染嗰批40-60歲嘅人好多都唔識分口罩架嘛！<br />\n你一堆堆擺出舖頭同人講話四層、保護性強嗰啲擺明有心誤導<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢啲活性碳口罩齋防塵防花粉隔臭<br />\n唔單止對防疫冇用仲會造成病毒累積</span><br />\n<br />\n收咗爐冇辦法鬧佢<br />\n咁唯有送份禮物比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gojNCSG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgojNCSG.jpg&h=ce7c223e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ytNzhSH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FytNzhSH.jpg&h=dd826039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日已經係第三日張紙仲喺度<br />\n而且每次行過都見到有街坊停低睇張紙<br />\n<br />\n小妹P牌仔唔知可以做到啲乜<br />\n求各位巴絲集合ＩＧ整理嘅力量幫手送吓禮物比啲無良害人藥房<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170765d2ebb1f66f240cc6dba1b986e2038504e0","tid":1844180,"uid":259055,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:57:42.000Z","msg":"裝修，要喺表格上原因應列明為「發災難財」"},{"pid":"447e7b596f6efafcdb2404b61e4a20cf2a3f5444","tid":1844180,"uid":339062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"170765d2ebb1f66f240cc6dba1b986e2038504e0","tid":1844180,"uid":259055,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:57:42.000Z","msg":"裝修，要喺表格上原因應列明為「發災難財」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:59:11.000Z","msg":"發財都算......賣假口罩會害死人架<img src=\"/asse